  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/ocd-combined-enriched">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology"/>
    <rdfs:label>OCD Ontology - Combined with Lexical Enrichment and External Mappings</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment>This comprehensive OCD ontology combines: (1) Base hand-crafted OCD concepts from domain experts, (2) Rich lexical enrichment using OntoLex vocabulary providing synonyms and alternative forms, (3) External semantic mappings to WordNet, OBO ontologies, and other knowledge bases. The ontology maintains focus on core OCD concepts while providing extensive semantic annotations for natural language processing, semantic search, and knowledge integration applications.</rdfs:comment>
    <dc1:created>2025-07-29</dc1:created>
    <dc1:creator>Combined from multiple sources</dc1:creator>
    <dc1:description>Generated by combining 458 base triples, 3020 lexical enrichment triples, and 9387 external mapping triples.</dc1:description>
  </rdf:Description>
