  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/ocd#Trichotillomania">
    <rdfs:comment>Trichotillomania, or Hair-Pulling Disorder, is categorized as one of the Obsessive-Compulsive and Related Disorders (OCRDs) in the DSM-5. It is characterized by recurrent hair-pulling resulting in hair loss.</rdfs:comment>
