  <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GSSO_007247">
    <obo:IAO_0000115 xml:lang="en">Sexual suggestiveness is visual, verbal, written or behavioral material or action with sexual undertones implying sexual intent in order to provoke sexual arousal. There are variations in the perception and display of sexual suggestiveness, including but not limited to gender, culture and generation.</obo:IAO_0000115>
