  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/ocd#hasInterferenceLevel">
    <rdfs:comment>The object property hasInterferenceLevel identifies the extent to which a behavior, activity, intrusive thought, or urge interferes with an individual's daily functioning. It connects the subject (behavior, activity, thought, or urge) to its corresponding interference level assessment.</rdfs:comment>
