  <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GSSO_012672">
    <obo:IAO_0000115 xml:lang="en">A popular misconception, cliché, and meme that refers to the fact that some nonbinary persons have non-traditional names, such as those of inanimate objects like "Sock", "River", or "Moss".</obo:IAO_0000115>
