  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/ocd#Doubt_Obsession">
    <rdfs:comment>OCI: Even when I do something very carefully I feel that it is not quite right. After I have done things, I have persistent doubts about whether I really did them. After doing something carefully, I still have the impression I haven’t finished it.</rdfs:comment>
