    <obo:IAO_0000115 xml:lang="en">A pseudoscientific media hypothesis which proposed that a growing number of Japanese adults have lost interest in sexual activity and have also lost interest in romantic love, dating and marriage. Following a report in The Guardian, the theory gained widespread attention in English media outlets in 2013, and was subsequently refuted by several journalists and bloggers.</obo:IAO_0000115>
