  <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0046959">
    <obo:IAO_0000115>A decrease in a behavioral response to a repeated stimulus. This is exemplified by the failure of a person to show a startle response to a loud noise that has been repeatedly presented.</obo:IAO_0000115>
  </rdf:Description>
