  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://www.w3.org/2006/03/wn/wn20/instances/synset-comfortable-adjective-2">
    <ns4:gloss xml:lang="en-us">(free from stress or conducive to mental ease; having or affording peace of mind; "was settled in a comfortable job, one for which he was well prepared"; "the comfortable thought that nothing could go wrong"; "was comfortable in his religious beliefs"; "she's a comfortable person to be with"; "she felt comfortable with her fiance's parents")</ns4:gloss>
