    <ns4:gloss xml:lang="en-us">((figurative) a carefully thought out strategy for achieving an objective in war or politics or business or personal affairs; "newscasters speculated about the President's game plan for an invasion")</ns4:gloss>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://www.w3.org/2006/03/wn/wn20/instances/synset-unbefitting-adjectivesatellite-1">
