    <ns4:gloss xml:lang="en-us">(be left; of persons, questions, problems, results, evidence, etc.; "There remains the question of who pulled the trigger"; "Carter remains the only President in recent history under whose Presidency the U.S. did not fight a war")</ns4:gloss>
